Tomlinson’s Wake – Event with Randy Wayne White at NOVA 535
Tombolo Books Presents: Tomlinson’s Wake – Event with Randy Wayne White at NOVA 535
Doors: 6:30pm | Event: 7:00pm
Parking and Directions
to NOVA 535
535 Dr. MLK Jr. Street North, St. Pete, FL 33701
More Info and Tickets
From New York Times bestselling author Randy Wayne White, the latest thriller following Doc Ford and his perilous journey into Mesoamerica after a world-shattering earthquake threatens his squad’s safety—and all of their lives.
Tombolo Books is thrilled to welcome back NYT bestselling and award-winning Florida author Randy Wayne White to launch the latest installment in his Doc Ford series,
Tomlinson’s Wake
!
======================
NOVA 535 is a 105 year old building, now the #1 rated venue in Tampa St. Pete. Our 5-star venue brings your unique vision to life with our stress free experience. Start planning your special event
HERE
